    "Description": "Fabric — lightweight modding toolchain for Minecraft Java Edition. Ideal for mods like Lithium, Sodium, and carpet.",
    "Author": "ogultra",
    "AuthorName": "OGUltra",
    "Image": "ghcr.io/hydren-dev/yolks:java",
